Class AudioFileRef

java.lang.Object
  cowrat.recoled.audio.AudioFileRef
Deprecated. These JMF-based classes have been dropped in favour of our own implementations. Use cowrat.recplaj.recorder.Recorder for audio recording and cowrat.rexplore.hnm.MakeHanmerProfile for activity logging (post-processing) instead. THIS PACKAGE IS NO LONGER USED IN RECOLED AND WILL SOON BE REMOVED.
